%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber

actor SU as Startup User
participant UI as Innovation UI
participant BFF as Innovation BFF
participant SERVICE as Innovation Service
participant OPENTEXT as MSIL OpenText DMS
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS Read schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
participant NS as Notification Service

SU ->> UI: Open Startup Landing (Applications / Projects / Programs)
UI ->> BFF: getStartupDashboard(userId)

BFF ->> SERVICE: fetchStartupDashboard(userId)
SERVICE ->> READDB: Get applications, projects, program invites, notifications
READDB -->> SERVICE: Dashboard data
SERVICE -->> BFF: Dashboard response
BFF -->> UI: Render landing page

alt Respond to Program Invite
    SU ->> UI: Click Yes / No on program invite
    UI ->> BFF: respondToInvite(programId, response)
    BFF ->> SERVICE: saveInviteResponse()
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: UPDATE program_invite_status
    SERVICE ->> KAFKA: Publish ProgramInviteResponded
    KAFKA ->> NS: Notify Program Manager
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Response saved
    BFF -->> UI: Update invite status
else Open Startup Preview
    SU ->> UI: Click Application / Program
    UI ->> BFF: getStartupPreview(startupId)
    BFF ->> SERVICE: fetchStartupPreview()
    SERVICE ->> READDB: Get stage, documents, comments, pending actions
    READDB -->> SERVICE: Preview data
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Preview response
    BFF -->> UI: Render preview

    alt Upload Pending Documents
        SU ->> UI: Upload documents and click Submit
        UI ->> BFF: uploadDocuments(files)
        BFF ->> OPENTEXT: Store documents
        OPENTEXT -->> BFF: document_ids
        BFF ->> SERVICE: saveDocumentMetadata(startupId, document_ids)
        SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT document metadata
        SERVICE ->> KAFKA: Publish StartupDocumentsSubmitted
        KAFKA ->> NS: Notify PM / Ecosystem Partner
        SERVICE -->> BFF: Upload success
        BFF -->> UI: Refresh document list and clear pending actions
    end
end